{
  "texts": [
    "The documents were annotated in two phases.",
    "The first annotation phase was performed by three annotators.",
    "Training documents were randomly sampled from post-2017 AP-HP medical records to bias the distribution and better fit the model to more recent documents.",
    "Test documents were sampled without constraint to evaluate performance on all documents in the CDW.",
    "Annotated entities are listed and described in ►Table 1."
  ]
}